title: Tadge Goods Windproof Travel Umbrella with Automatic Open/Close (Black) Rain Resistant Canopy with Teflon Coating | Wind Proof Durability | Includes Carry Bag
feature: TRUE WIND AND RAIN PROTECTION – Each beautiful umbrella offers a stronger, wider, more durable canopy with Teflon coating to keep you drier when weather gets heavy.

STRONGER, LARGE CANOPY COVERAGE – This outdoor umbrella provides better shoulder to knee protection with a wide, reinforced design made with 10 total fiberglass ribs! DO NOT BUY UMBRELLAS WITH 9 or LESS RIBS (very weak)!
AUTOMATIC OPEN/CLOSE BUTTON – Each sun, rain and windproof travel umbrella is fitted with a push-button handle that lets you quickly unfurl or store it in seconds.
SLIP-RESISTANT GRIP – Lightweight and travel friendly, each windproof umbrella features a non-slip comfortable grip for better handling and travel storage bag.
TADGE GOODS 100% SATISFACTION GUARANTEE – Every travel umbrella that we create is made with superior craftsmanship and reliability, and comes backed by true quality assurance.
